results.occurrenceRemarks: I found this insect in my room. It was hopping around the floor. It also tried to fly with it's wing but it could not actually fly. I think it's wings were damaged because whenever it tried to fly, it was falling onto it's left side over and over again. It was 4 cm long, and 2 cm wide
Out foraging in daylight and heading towards another calling nearby.
